{"type":"message","id":"70845e90","parentId":"deb548b5","timestamp":"2026-03-29T02:20:18.705Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-29 10:20 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 执行企业数字化相关行业信息搜索任务：\n\n1. 搜索以下4个领域的最新动态（2025-2026年）：\n   - 企业数字化转型最新政策和趋势\n   - 智能安防行业动态和技术趋势\n   - 网络系统集成行业动态\n   - IT运维服务行业发展趋势\n\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息，每条包含：\n   - 标题\n   - 核心内容摘要\n   - 对道简网络这类To B科技服务企业的参考意义\n\n3. 将结果保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n请使用web_search技能进行搜索，输出格式为Markdown。"}],"timestamp":1774750818702}}
{"type":"message","id":"58c2d190","parentId":"70845e90","timestamp":"2026-03-29T02:20:22.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to search for industry information in 4 areas related to enterprise digitalization. Let me first read the web_search skill to understand how to use it properly.","thinkingSignature":"8fbf31309fe10a2efc89eed4858446c29f9e219eab3bf8b0772fb92a179fac9c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w1vgut9i02ho_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":74,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42192,"totalTokens":42383,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.00008879999999999999,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0050630399999999996,"total":0.005186939999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774750818704}}
{"type":"message","id":"6cbb07ff","parentId":"58c2d190","timestamp":"2026-03-29T02:20:22.840Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_w1vgut9i02ho_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774750822837}}
{"type":"message","id":"555d9a7a","parentId":"6cbb07ff","timestamp":"2026-03-29T02:20:28.156Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll use the web search skill to search for each of the 4 areas. Let me run all 4 searches in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"e292e580ee6e87b3fe9a60fa6a52ce388a0dc54a504a76e03d084fddf9f5f611"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cpe4nfoxqrxx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2025 2026 最新政策趋势\" --output json","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cpe4nfoxqrxx_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 技术趋势 2025 2026\" --output json","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cpe4nfoxqrxx_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成行业动态 2025 2026\" --output json","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cpe4nfoxqrxx_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业发展趋势 2025 2026\" --output json","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":907,"output":248,"cacheRead":41991,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43146,"cost":{"input":0.0002721,"output":0.00029759999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00125973,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00182943}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774750822840}}
